nce of this Agreement;\n\n2.2 Confidential Information shall not include:\n\ni) information which was known by a Party prior to receiving it from the other Party if this can be demonstrated by written record;", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1046, "end_char_idx": 1466, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "d65d9580-8e5d-45ca-859e-ecc42bc49518": {"__data__": {"id_": "d65d9580-8e5d-45ca-859e-ecc42bc49518", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "6ac0d9e0-7c90-4398-9182-8718d2551d0e", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "9a6e838a2954f3f09cc70dbf80a0825dd704251b6b00c2fb6a862993841c5196", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "063959c0-6456-4565-97de-525987a52032", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "3d2ef5bfcdb303994fbb9ab06be53898955ffd2ee71c50efe288f246eb0ae82e", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "f621b411-6cb6-4e98-bbb8-6817cd03a764", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "5338061103d1e52afda35bdc181af4550d444469d7a0b7677da7d4076e86bc8f", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "ii) information which at the time of disclosure is in the public domain or which is published after disclosure or otherwise becomes part of  the public domain without breach of this Agreement;\n\niii) information which the Party can show was received from a third party who did not to the best knowledge of the Party receive the information,\n\n directly or indirectly, from the other Party under any obligation of confidentiality;\nDOCUMENT NO.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1468, "end_char_idx": 1908, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "f621b411-6cb6-4e98-bbb8-6817cd03a764": {"__data__"