ype": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "5338061103d1e52afda35bdc181af4550d444469d7a0b7677da7d4076e86bc8f", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "731b099a-fc00-4a32-91a1-c99f8322d7f7", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "86c34afaeaa064aba5dbc74a1c6e457a3e9e1e758a2f0a0825cd4f2e4df3f80b", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "private and confidential;\n\nii) to take all steps necessary to preserve such confidentiality and secrecy;\n\niii) to prevent disclosure of any such Confidential Information to any third party;\n\niv) to use the Confidential Information solely for the purpose set out in Section 1;\n\nv) to disclose the Confidential Information only to those of its directors,\n\n employees and consultants who need the Confidential Information to conduct tasks in relation to the purpose set out in Section 1;", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2359, "end_char_idx": 2843, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "731b099a-fc00-4a32-91a1-c99f8322d7f7": {"__data__": {"id_": "731b099a-fc00-4a32-91a1-c99f8322d7f7", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "6ac0d9e0-7c90-4398-9182-8718d2551d0e", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "9a6e838a2954f3f09cc70dbf80a0825dd704251b6b00c2fb6a862993841c5196", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "0773b928-7609-4f31-bfe7-401eaf24c017", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "570acc3be28c896339c6da99b5ae1e4bbc5f11fd4ebf9f06108aad077b264e06", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "4714ae8a-c0d2-4d09-8763-e3e43b95fe51", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "a055e180e12b5d513e7fa7451fde22af2655dc0a586a93a7c549582059ac6193", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "vi) to ascertain that each person who receives Confidential Information is made aware of and comply with this Agreement;\n\n and\n\nvii) to immediately upon request deliver to the other Party all Confidential Information that belong to that Party in any form without retaining any copies thereof,\n\n or, at the other Party\u2019s option, certify in writing that all copies of such information have been destroyed.\n\n4.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2845, "end_char_idx": 3252, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "4714ae8a-c0d2-4d09-8763-e3e43b95fe51": {"__data__": {"id_": "4714ae8a-c0d2-4d09-8763-e3e43b95fe51", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "6ac0d9e0-7c90-4398-9182-8718d2551d0e", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "9a6e838a2954f3f09cc70dbf80a0825dd704251b6b00c2fb6a862993841c5196", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "731b099a-fc00-4a32-91a1-c99f8322d7f7", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "86c34afaeaa064aba5dbc74a1c6e457a3e9e1e758a2f0a0825cd4f2e4df3f80b", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "56020c06-7c57-45a4-8c2c-c6bbe2ef1f31", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "cf39b392d5eb04ff56dfe10eec8ca52291c5b76e0a6e4b7c96ddea057ab321aa", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Disclosure under mandatory law\n\nIf either Party due to mandatory law is forced to disclose information which would otherwise be considered as Confidential Information, the Party shall prior to the disclosure inform the other Party hereof and the Parties shall mutually decide how to minimize the negative consequences thereof.\n\n5. Indemnification\n\nThe Parties undertake to reimburse, indemnify and hold the other Party harmless from any damages, loss or expense incurred by it as a result of either Party violating the terms of this Agreement.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 3253, "end_char_idx": 3796, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "56020c06-7c57-45a4-8c2c-c6bbe2ef1f31": {"__data__": {"id_": "56020c06-7c57-45a4-8c2c-c6bbe2ef1f31", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "6ac0d9e0-7c90-4398-9182-8718d2551d0e", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "9a6e838a2954f3f09cc70dbf80a0825dd704251b6b00c2fb6a862993841c5196", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "4714ae8a-c0d2-4d09-8763-e3e43b95fe51", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "a055e180e12b5d513e7fa7451fde22af2655dc0a586a93a7c549582059ac6193", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "8637ebce-1df6-48d8-848d-c008b6235820", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "0fea51f520cf15b69ba5a10444428b64d4b2f133faa3645a0f3119c1c1de883e", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "6. No license\n\nNothing in this Agreement shall be deemed to constitute or to imply the granting of any license, immunity or other right under any intellectual property right of either Party, or to\nDOCUMENT NO. HDX4-51-130 Replaces SCM-0021\nLEGAL#1597040V1\nprovide a commitment of any kind by either Party to enter into further agreements with the other Party.\n\n7.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 3798, "end_char_idx": 4161, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "8637ebce-1df6-48d8-848d-c008b6235820": {"__data__": {"id_": "8637ebce-1df6-48d8-848d-c008b6235820", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "6ac0d9e0-7c90-